Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: In this area of Williston, there is a ton of residential density. This combined with a prime location and lack of office space available in Williston makes for a great opportunity to expand with the city. Williston has continued to grow steadily since oil boomed and infrastructure has been put in place to accommodate the increasing population and demand. The community has exceptional schools, a dynamic professional community, and an array of off-site amenities such as lodging, restaurants, retail, fitness and recreational opportunities.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE and Chance Lindsey as the exclusive marketing brokers, are pleased to offer this class A office and retail space. With great views and endless possibilities for space configurations, this is a fantastic opportunity to be in the highest density area in Williston. Harvest Plaza is simple to get to with safe and easy access and ample parking on site.
